  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will conduct a brief educational intervention to pregnant women who have
      not yet received the influenza vaccine in this pregnancy to improve the uptake of seasonal
      influenza vaccine.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
